This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language modeling and dialogue systems. Additionally, it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses LSTM-based methods and neural models. It may also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the integration of multiple neural models. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves retrieving information from a knowledge-base.
